data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the Canterbury Estates Subdivision. This exquisite residence offers a lifestyle of luxury and comfort, blending modern amenities with timeless elegance. Spanning across a generous half-acre lot in a serene cul-de-sac setting, this meticulously crafted home features 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, including a bedroom and bathroom on the main levelCoa perfect retreat for guests or multigenerational living. Step inside to discover wide plank, oak hardwood floors gracing the main level and creating a warm ambiance. The open floorplan seamlessly connects the heart of the home, where a majestic stone fireplace anchors the 2-story Great Room where everyone can gather for cozy evenings. Entertain with ease in the expansive kitchen, complete with a large pantry, granite countertops, island and Stainless Steel appliances. A keeping room/breakfast area leads to a spacious deck, ideal for al fresco dining, grilling and enjoying the serene views of the large fenced backyard. Formal Living and Dining Rooms provide elegant spaces for hosting guests, while multiple areas offer versatility for home offices or creative pursuits. The wet bar and ButlerCOs Pantry provide space for effortless serving when hosting friends and family. Escape to the OwnerCOs suite, a luxurious sanctuary featuring a large sitting room, outdoor private deck. The renovated spa-like bath offers separate vanities, a walk in shower and soaking tub Co truly a haven for relaxation. The oversized walk-in closet provides ample space for the fashionista. Explore the vibrant surroundings with close proximity to an array of restaurants, Kennesaw Mountain, and Marietta Country Club, ensuring endless opportunities for leisure and recreation. Additional features include a full, daylight basement with a large paver patio, a 3-car garage for ample storage, and 3-sides brick construction with stone accents for timeless curb appeal. The main level laundry and entry zone will keep your home tidy even with the most active lifestyles. Canterbury Estates offers a medium size community and amenities include a pool and clubhouse. YouCOll love the quiet neighborhood and friendly neighbors. Don't miss your chance to experience the epitome of luxury living in Kennesaw, where every detail has been thoughtfully curated to enhance your lifestyle. Welcome home to 1710 Nemours DrCowhere elegance meets comfort, and memories are made.
